<codeline><highlight class="normal">This<sp/>package<sp/>is<sp/>responsible<sp/>to<sp/>control<sp/>a<sp/>mobile<sp/>robot<sp/>when<sp/>receives<sp/>a<sp/>`go_to_point`<sp/>command<sp/>from<sp/>the<sp/>user.</highlight></codeline>
